name: British Gypsum Gyproc Moisture Resistant Tapered Edge 2400mm x 1200mm x 12.5mm

Its silicone additives along with its water repellent liners help achieve a product that is perfect for use in, Bathrooms and kitchens where levels of humidity are significantly higher. This impressive plasterboard absorbs less than 5% of water, provides great fire protection and acoustic insulation where needed. This product is ideal for semi exposed areas and is a must for any Bathroom or kitchen construction.

name: Sika Wintermix 5LTR
description: Sika Wintermix Admixture is an air entraining, chloride free, liquid admixture for mortar and concrete which also acts as an accelerator for work in sub - zero temperatures, with increased frost resistance during setting. Sika Wintermix improves workability, even in cold weather as well as freeze/thaw resistance in bricklaying mortars, thus eliminating the need for a separate frost proofer. Sika Wintermix can be used as an air entraining, water reducing, admixture and accelerator/frost proofer for brick and block laying mortar, render (internal and external) and concrete Sika Wintermix is also suitable for load bearing brickwork, block laying, external and internal rendering, pointing/repointing brickwork and floor screeds. Due to the embedded metal, Sika Wintermix is non-corrosive to embedded metal and can also replace Lime in the mix, reducing the possibility of lime bloom and efflorescence. Sika Wintermix also benefits from reduced shrinkage, with in turn reduces cracking and crazing.

name: Ulti-Mate® Stick-Fit® Wood Screws Trade Assortment Qty 1000
description:
These high-performance Ulti-Mate® wood screws are built for strength. Featuring a patented PSD® drive system to enable smooth, stable driving and Stick-Fit® one-handed installation, this trade pack includes 1,000 screws in five sizes from 25-70mm.
A thick core diameter ensures superior strength throughout the body of the screw, and also under the head area. With a sharp point and prominent thread at the tip, you’ll get a rapid start and immediate thread engagement – this saves time and effort, helping you drive more screws per charge if using a cordless tool.
A slotted shank reduces wood splitting, and a countersunk head complete with ribs ensures a flush finish. Screws 40mm and shorter don’t have the ribs, to make them hinge-compatible. As well as five popular sizes, the pack also includes five Stick-Fit® driver bits. A high-quality Stick-Fit driver bit is included in every single box of Ulti-Mate Wood Screws. The screws also feature a type-17 point to drive through the hardest timber, a double-angle countersunk head for a neat finish and a wide, deep single thread for rapid insertion and strong holding power.

name: Evo-Stick 30812633 Waterproof Wall Tile Adhesive 10L Natural
description:
Evo-Stick Waterproof Wall Tile Adhesive is a ready-mixed, mould-resistant, waterproof tile adhesive suitable for fixing ceramic wall tiles to most types of sound, and interior surfaces.

As the adhesive is waterproof, it is ideal for use in areas subject to infrequent wetting and condensation, such as kitchen and bathroom walls. This showerproof wall tile adhesive can also be applied directly onto existing tiles for convenience.

Suitable materials: Suitable for fixing onto most internal surfaces including plaster, plasterboard, glazed tiles, brick, cement, cement renders, and tile backer boards.

Suitable tiles: For fixing ceramic wall tiles.

Available as a 10L waterproof wall tile adhesive. The adhesive is supplied in a post-consumer recycled (PCR) bucket to reduce the impact of the product on the environment.

name: Bostik J115 Smooth Finish White Grout 5kg
description:
Bostik J115 Flexible Smooth Finish Grout is a professional quality, cementitious polymer modified grout for walls and floors. It is formulated to provide narrow and wide joints.
This flexible white grout is an easy clean off, non slump formulation and sets in 12 hours to a very hard finish. It is also mould and efflorescence resistant.
Suitable for use with a variety of tile types including ceramic, porcelain, natural stone, mosaic, marble and quarry tiles. It is suitable for joints between 2mm and 15mm for both interior and exterior use.

name: Bostik MC250 Vitri-Flex Rapid Set White Wall & Floor Tile Adhesive 20kg
description:
Bostik MC250 Vitri-Flex is a fast-setting, flexible wall and floor tile adhesive in white. It is suitable for bonding ceramic tiles, quarry tiles, porcelain, vitrified tiles, natural stone and mosaics to wall and floors.

This white, rapid-setting wall and floor tile adhesive is formulated for fast track installation and enables tiles to be grouted in approximately 2 to 3 hours after fixing, depending on conditions. It provides excellent grip and adhesion.

Bostik Vitri-Flex tile adhesive is suitable for most interior and exterior installations including more demanding installations, such as use with underfloor heating and areas subject to limited vibration. When fully cured the adhesive is suitable for permanently wet areas such as showers. It will bond to concrete, plaster, sand/cement render and screeds, blockwork, brickwork, glazed surfaces, vinyl tiles, plywood overlay and more.

One of Bostik's best adhesives for vitrified tiles. Available in a 20kg bag.

name: Evo-Stick 30812628 Instant Grab Wall Tile Adhesive 5L Natural
description:
Evo-Stick Instant Grab Wall Tile Adhesive for is a fast-acting, ready-mixed tile adhesive for fixing ceramic wall tiles on dry, internal walls. Its showerproof properties make it a suitable wall tile adhesive for areas subject to some splashing and condensation, such as in kitchens and bathrooms.

The instant tile adhesive is easy-to-use and can be used to tile onto most substrates, including existing tiles. 

Suitable materials: For fixing onto most internal surfaces including plaster, plasterboard, glazed tiles, brick, cement, cement renders and tile backer boards.

name: Grabo Pro-Lifter 20 Cordless Digital Vacuum Lifter with Battery & Charger GRAB300
description:
"The GRABO Pro is our most advanced vacuum lifter, perfect for the safe and easy handling of Tiles, Paving Slabs, Glass, Sheet Metal, Wood, Doors, Sheet Materials, Rough Concrete, Plasterboard, and even Household Appliances and Furniture. Designed with ergonomics in mind, it ensures improved grip and reduced fatigue during the handling of heavy objects.

Equipped with a smart digital pressure sensor, a digital display, and intelligent weight and pressure settings, the GRABO Pro offers enhanced functionality. With the inclusion of an auto on/off switch, the GRABO Pro continuously monitors and maintains the optimal suction level, activating or deactivating as needed. The smart digital gauge provides a visual grip indication, displaying both bar/PSI measurements and the maximum weight that the GRABO Pro can safely lift in kilograms or pounds, ensuring safe and efficient operations.

The Grabo Pro comes fully equipped with a tough zipped carry case, standard seal, battery, and charger"

name: Grabo Plus Cordless Vacuum Lifter With Battery & Charger GRAB220
description:
The Grabo Plus is the original hand-held, battery-powered vacuum lifter. Using patented technology it revolutionizes the handling of various materials such as tiles, stone, concrete, drywall, plywood, windows, and furniture. The Grabo is versatile, allowing for material handling of glass, sheet metal, windows, doors, hardwood products, timber, beams, plastic sheets, tiles, rough concrete, plasterboard, and even household appliances and furniture.

The Grabo Plus offers immense benefits to individuals involved in lifting and moving heavy objects. Whether it's pavers working with heavy stones, tilers seeking precision placement, or removal companies dealing with awkward furniture, the Grabo allows you to put a handle on almost anything! The original Grabo Plus offers manual controls but matches the 170kg lifting capacity of the Grabo Pro.

The Grabo Plus reduces the risk of strain and injury associated with manual lifting of heavy objects. It allows for a more controlled and ergonomic handling of materials, minimizing the potential for accidents or musculoskeletal issues. By reducing the physical strain on workers and providing a secure grip on materials, the Grabo Plus Tool promotes a safer working environment.

Angle grinder with diamond blade and case.

name: Grabo Rockseal Foam Seal GRAB109
description: The RockSeal is made from durable, extra-thick foam, allowing it to form a strong seal around uneven material. RockSeal is compatible with all GRABO models and can be swapped from the standard GRABO seal in seconds.

name: Grabo Pro-Lifter 20 Cordless Digital Vacuum Lifter with Battery & Charger GRAB300
description:
"The GRABO Pro is our most advanced vacuum lifter, perfect for the safe and easy handling of Tiles, Paving Slabs, Glass, Sheet Metal, Wood, Doors, Sheet Materials, Rough Concrete, Plasterboard, and even Household Appliances and Furniture. Designed with ergonomics in mind, it ensures improved grip and reduced fatigue during the handling of heavy objects.

Equipped with a smart digital pressure sensor, a digital display, and intelligent weight and pressure settings, the GRABO Pro offers enhanced functionality. With the inclusion of an auto on/off switch, the GRABO Pro continuously monitors and maintains the optimal suction level, activating or deactivating as needed. The smart digital gauge provides a visual grip indication, displaying both bar/PSI measurements and the maximum weight that the GRABO Pro can safely lift in kilograms or pounds, ensuring safe and efficient operations.

The Grabo Pro comes fully equipped with a tough zipped carry case, standard seal, battery, and charger"

name: Grabo Plus Cordless Vacuum Lifter With Battery & Charger GRAB220
description:
The Grabo Plus is the original hand-held, battery-powered vacuum lifter. Using patented technology it revolutionizes the handling of various materials such as tiles, stone, concrete, drywall, plywood, windows, and furniture. The Grabo is versatile, allowing for material handling of glass, sheet metal, windows, doors, hardwood products, timber, beams, plastic sheets, tiles, rough concrete, plasterboard, and even household appliances and furniture.

The Grabo Plus offers immense benefits to individuals involved in lifting and moving heavy objects. Whether it's pavers working with heavy stones, tilers seeking precision placement, or removal companies dealing with awkward furniture, the Grabo allows you to put a handle on almost anything! The original Grabo Plus offers manual controls but matches the 170kg lifting capacity of the Grabo Pro.

The Grabo Plus reduces the risk of strain and injury associated with manual lifting of heavy objects. It allows for a more controlled and ergonomic handling of materials, minimizing the potential for accidents or musculoskeletal issues. By reducing the physical strain on workers and providing a secure grip on materials, the Grabo Plus Tool promotes a safer working environment.

name: Grabo Replacement Foam Seal GRAB106
description: The standard replacement seal for both the Grabo Pro and Grabo Plus. We recommend changing your Grabo seal at least every six months or sooner with heavy use.

name: STANLEY FATMAX TradeLift
description: The STANLEY FATMAX TradeLift is a versatile handheld tool for lifting, levelling, holding and spreading of heavy or awkward objects such as appliances, sheet materials or furniture ï¿½ a real life saver when you're working alone. Engineered for safety, this professional, heavy-duty tool enables easy hands-free lifting up to 150kg, to a maximum height of 220mm. The TradeLiftï¿½ is perfect for jobs like hanging doors, installing kitchen cabinets and appliances and fitting windows in all environments, with enclosed metal plate housing to enhance durability and prevent dust entering the tool. The robust lifting tool can be operated by hand or foot, with an ergonomic overmoulded handle providing extra grip, comfort, and control. A fine adjuster lowers the load by up to 2.5mm per toggle for precision levelling and spacing, with a full release button safely recessed to avoid accidental activation. The large base plate with angled edge slides easily under low objects and reduces the risk of tipping, with four screwholes countersunk into the base to anchor the lift for maximum stability.

name: DeWalt 18V XR Li-ion Cordless Jigsaw - Body Only DCS331N-XJ
description: The DeWalt 18V XR Li-ion Jigsaw is part of the intelligent XR lithium-ion platform designed for efficiency and making applications faster. The powerful and highly efficient fan cooled motor with replaceable brushes, delivers up to 3000 strokes per minute, making cutting applications faster. The 3 sided pendulum action feature controls the aggressiveness and smoothness of cuts.

name: DeWalt 18V Xr Circular Saw Body Only DCS391N-XJ
description: DeWalt 18V XR Circular Saw Bare Unit, high speed output of 5150 rpm and Ultra thin kerf Blade allows for long runtimes. name: Stanley Junior Sawhorse Twin Pack
description: Sawhorse Twin Pack - maximum load 170kg

name: V-TUF 240V M Class Mini Dust Extraction Vaccum Cleaner
description: The V-TÜF M CLASS MINI helps you tackle dust at the source. Connect it directly to your power tools or sweep up and enjoy a dust-free environment. The V-TÜF®M CLASS MINI is M-Class Rated, the ‘Minimum Requirement’ for construction sites. Unrated vacuum cleaners are extremely dangerous as respirable dust can pass through the motor and be pumped back into the air. This dust then remains airborne for up to 8 hours, where it can be inhaled directly into your lung chamber, where it will remain forever. Approximately 700 people in the UK die every year due to illness relating to the inhalation of respirable dust. Needless to say, this dust also damages your vacuum motor. The V-TÜF®M CLASS MINI offers you affordable compliance and protection from common dust-related health issues! The new M CLASS MINI is a keystone that helps V-TUF achieve its mission: To save and improve the lives of those in their line of duty. Ideal for: Construction & woodworking Industries. No reason to not embrace the M Class protection.

name: ToughBuilt® Reload Utility Knife + 2 Blade Mags
description: The ToughBuilt® Reload Utility Knife is an innovative quick-change tool expertly crafted from professional-grade materials with a groundbreaking, patented mechanism that accepts spring-loaded blade magazines and autoloads a fresh blade with the flick of a switch. Replacing worn blades is safe and easy with a blade release button that removes used blades before loading a new one by simply pulling the actuator back and flicking it forward again. With a simple press of the magazine release, a positive, spring-loaded magazine ejector drops the magazine away from the tool or into an open hand. A new magazine can then be loaded inside, making it easy to switch from one type of blade to another in a flash. All Toughbuilt mags have an indicator switch. Positions 1, 2 or 3 remind the Pro what type of blade is loaded in a magazine without having to remove the magazine from a pouch or pocket. The Reload Knife is quality constructed from smooth aluminum alloy and zinc alloy for corrosion resistance. It is wrapped in a rugged, grippy, non-slip soft-touch rubber housing to protect the tool from shocks and drops while creating a more dexterous hand purchase on the instrument. The finger guard helps keep pros safe while cutting tough materials. It includes a five-pack of ToughBuilt universal straight-edge blades and a five-pack of ToughBuilt specialized hook blades that use a smart, precision-milled, proprietary edge design. The straight edge blades work interchangeably with the Reload Knife and the ToughBuilt Scraper Utility Knife or any standard utility knife.

description: Speedfit Layflat Polybutylene barrier pipe has even greater flexibility making the system very easy to handle and worry free. name: JG Speedfit 90° Equal Elbow Elbow 15mm
description: Speedfit push-fit plastic fitting for the connection of plastic and copper pipe. Simply push the fitting fully onto the pipe and twist the plastic nut clockwise to lock in place. Should the need arise to demount the connection unlock the nut and push the collet towards the body of the fitting and pull the pipe to release. The fitting ensures an easier working environment in confined places and removes the need for hot works on site. Installation can be reduced by around 40% against traditional fixing methods. Note: with all plastic pipes the relevant manufacturer’s pipe insert is required. Designed, manufactured and assembled in the UK by John Guest Speedfit.

description: Deck-Tite's unique thread pitch to core size ratio offers the perfect balance between ease of insertion and pull-out retention whilst increasing the core's sheer strength to match the thread pitch.
